<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" ><generator uri="https://jekyllrb.com/" version="4.3.2">Jekyll</generator><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/feed.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml" /><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" /><updated>2024-12-25T21:28:52-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/feed.xml</id><title type="html">Hermosawave Photography</title><subtitle>A series of daily landscape photographs by Daniel Sofer, 20 years running.</subtitle><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><entry><title type="html">Holiday Plaza</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241224/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Holiday Plaza" /><published>2024-12-24T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2024-12-24T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/pier-plaza</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241224/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Hernosa’s Pier Plaza, lit up at sunset on Christmas Eve.
</p>

<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">ホリデー・プラザ</span>
クリスマスイブの夕暮れ時にライトアップされたハーモサのピア・プラザ。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Dusk" /><category term="Pier Plaza" /><category term="Light Up" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Hernosa’s Pier Plaza, lit up at sunset on Christmas Eve.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2412_A7R00077_ai-2.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2412_A7R00077_ai-2.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Holiday Reflections</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241218/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Holiday Reflections" /><published>2024-12-18T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2024-12-18T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/pier</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241218/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Dusk at the Manhattan Beach Pier, lit up with holiday lights, reflecting on the beach at low tide.
</p>

<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">ホリデー・リフレクションズ</span>
マンハッタン・ビーチ・ピアで夕暮れを眺めています。ホリデー・イルミネーションで彩られ、干潮時にはその光がビーチに反射します。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Manhattan Beach" /><category term="Dusk" /><category term="Piers" /><category term="Beach" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Dusk at the Manhattan Beach Pier, lit up with holiday lights, reflecting on the beach at low tide.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2412_A7R09945.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2412_A7R09945.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Afterglow</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241217/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Afterglow" /><published>2024-12-17T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2024-12-17T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/mbpier</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241217/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
   Taken through the supports of the Manhattan Beach Pier, a family on the sand watches the afterglow reflect on the beach. During these extreme low tides, the beach becomes like a mirror.
</p>

<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">残照</span>
マンハッタンビーチピアの支柱を通って撮影された、砂浜で家族が残照がビーチに反射する様子を見守っています。このような極端な干潮時には、ビーチがまるで鏡のようになります。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Manhattan Beach" /><category term="Dusk" /><category term="Piers" /><category term="Beach" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Taken through the supports of the Manhattan Beach Pier, a family on the sand watches the afterglow reflect on the beach. During these extreme low tides, the beach becomes like a mirror.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2412_A7R09940.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2412_A7R09940.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Sailboat Sunset</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241215/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Sailboat Sunset" /><published>2024-12-15T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2024-12-15T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/sailboat</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241215/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
   A sailboat passes by at sunset, at 9th St. in Hermosa Beach.
</p>

<p class="jp">
<!--<span class="title_jp"></span>-->
ハーモサビーチの 9th St.で、夕暮れ時にヨットが通り過ぎます。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Boats" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[A sailboat passes by at sunset, at 9th St. in Hermosa Beach.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2412_A7R09828.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2412_A7R09828.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Ripples in the Sand</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241214/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Ripples in the Sand" /><published>2024-12-14T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2024-12-14T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/huntington</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241214/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
The waves advancing and receding create lines and ripples on the sand, at extremely low tide in front of the Huntington Beach Pier.
</p>

<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">砂の波紋</span>
干潮時、ハンティントンビーチピアの前では、波が押し寄せたり引いたりして、砂に線や波紋を描きます。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Southern California" /><category term="Beach" /><category term="Low Tide" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[The waves advancing and receding create lines and ripples on the sand, at extremely low tide in front of the Huntington Beach Pier.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2412_A7R09756.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2412_A7R09756.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Point Vicente Sunset</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241212/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Point Vicente Sunset" /><published>2024-12-12T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2024-12-12T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/point-vicente</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241212/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
   After a rain, the sun sets behind the Point Vicente Lighthouse on the Palos Verdes Peninsula.
</p>

<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">ポイント・ビセンテの夕日</span>
雨上がり、パロスバーデス半島のポイント・ビセンテ灯台の向こうに日が沈む。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Palos Verdes" /><category term="Lighthouses" /><category term="Sunset" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[After a rain, the sun sets behind the Point Vicente Lighthouse on the Palos Verdes Peninsula.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2412_A7R09677-HDR.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2412_A7R09677-HDR.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Sunset</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241209/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Sunset" /><published>2024-12-09T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2024-12-09T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/sunset</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241209/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
   The end of a beautiful day.
</p>

<p class="jp">
<!--<span class="title_jp">濃霧</span>-->
美しい一日の終わり。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Beach" /><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Lifeguard Towers" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[The end of a beautiful day.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2412_A7R09623.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2412_A7R09623.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">22nd St.</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241208/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="22nd St." /><published>2024-12-08T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2024-12-08T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/22ndSt</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241208/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
   Beautiful sky, on the Strand in Hermosa Beach.
</p>

<p class="jp">
<!--<span class="title_jp">濃霧</span>-->
美しい空、ハーモサビーチのストランドにて。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Beach" /><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Strand" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Beautiful sky, on the Strand in Hermosa Beach.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2412_A7R09612.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2412_A7R09612.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Heavy Fog</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241206/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Heavy Fog" /><published>2024-12-06T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2024-12-06T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/foggy</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241206/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
   Heavy fog at the beach this morning.
</p>

<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">濃霧</span>
今朝の海岸は濃霧。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Redondo Beach" /><category term="Beach" /><category term="Fog" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Heavy fog at the beach this morning.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2412_A7R09558.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2412_A7R09558.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Beach Christmas</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241204/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Beach Christmas" /><published>2024-12-04T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2024-12-04T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/holiday-pier</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/241204/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
   Holiday lights at the Manhattan Beach Pier. A crescent Moon and Venus are visible in the sky.
</p>

<p class="jp">
<span class="title_jp">ビーチクリスマス</span>
マンハッタンビーチピアのホリデーイルミネーション。空には三日月と金星が見える。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Manhattan Beach" /><category term="Dusk" /><category term="Piers" /><category term="Lightup" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Holiday lights at the Manhattan Beach Pier. A crescent Moon and Venus are visible in the sky.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2412_A7R09539_ai_bright.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2024/2412_A7R09539_ai_bright.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry></feed>